snippet.description:
Something strange has been happening to Spinnin’ Sessions Radio. From time to time, ID tracks that aren’t supposed to be heard by the public mysteriously find their way into the episode. It seems like this phenomenon is called ‘The ID Leak’. Since the track has leaked anyway, can you help us figure out the artist/title of the track?
 
Listen to the full episode of Spinnin’ Sessions Radio #361 here: https://youtu.be/owOIKYh4jAo

Make sure to subscribe to Spinnin' Records: http://bit.do/spinnintv 
..and turn on notifications to stay updated with all new uploads!🔔
